title: Childhood Bride (English, Luna)
description: Coming back to his hometown in 7 years, this place has changed into a place that no man can resists, unlike what it used to be! A noona wearing a sexy female diver suit, up to his sexy mom’s friend with a mature figure that stimulates the hearts of men…! “The things we weren’t able to do back then… Shall we do it now?”
author: Yoo Wol
